<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_34539c0d-d140-4ab4-8065-1b3d61310dd8" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>D3D11</sptc><title id="_ca52e3eb-0527-4d88-a900-7def74fa5086">Pedestrian ramps</title><archive-num>2019: D2.10</archive-num><subclause id="_32f64bd4-ddcd-4201-aa6b-ac982932ef59" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_05ff43fe-d9c9-44ba-bcfd-33c2ecd16d8f">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1284_2.0.0.xml#_cfa6cc89-aa6c-4eaf-90e6-8aabe04b9c76" id="_198e0cfb-0004-4612-9192-5b78e2039398" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated ramp</xref> may be substituted for a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1285_2.1.0.xml#_c71e675e-d6e1-4612-8e59-381a56e224a8" id="_af07ff95-de4d-45d7-9e4a-ac7bd65c3c47" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated stairway</xref> if the construction enclosing the ramp and the width and ceiling height comply with the requirements for a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1285_2.1.0.xml#_c71e675e-d6e1-4612-8e59-381a56e224a8" id="_927da9e2-d644-44db-a809-3e9c71764859" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated stairway</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_3d18e207-498a-4f8b-9c1b-79f17615fd65" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_122341fe-0794-4f98-8e9b-1acbbb8952cb">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>A ramp serving as a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_ea4eccfc-b333-44ff-b4b6-7e585e3b98de" inv:access="external" scope="loc